\"everything\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"the treatment\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cupping is a type of therapy that creates suction against the skin using a variety of tools including plastic cups, ceramic, bamboo or glass cups.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cupping\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"a type\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"suction\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"the skin\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"a variety\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"tools\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"plastic cups\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"ceramic\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"bamboo\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"glass cups\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pressure is created inside the cup and the skin is pulled to promote blood flow to the area.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pressure\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"the cup\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"the skin\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"blood flow\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is also \\\"wet cupping\\\" where less suction is used, but afterwards small cuts are made across the skin and then a small amount of blood is taken.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"wet cupping\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"less suction\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"small cuts\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"the skin\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"a small amount\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where does cupping come from?\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cupping has been popular in a number of cultures including in China, Egypt and across the Middle East, and dates back thousands of years.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9869341071352661, \"rank\": 0.013196665672931136, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Egypt\", \"score\": 0.9124283172440125, \"rank\": 0.09542564519568991, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Egypt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Egypt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cupping\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"cultures\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"the Middle East\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it has recently become popular because of use by celebrities and athletes, who have influenced the use of the practice across the world.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"celebrities\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1807}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"the practice\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1852}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why does it leave a mark?\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mark\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The practice is supposed to draw fluid to the area, and the dark marks are because of broken blood vessels just under the skin, similar to a bruise.\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 2047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The practice\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"fluid\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"the dark marks\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"broken blood vessels\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"the skin\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"a bruise\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How did it become popular?\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cupping was in the spotlight in the 2016 Rio Olympics when the marks were spotted on Phelps' back, legs and shoulders.\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2162, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.999999997597115, \"rank\": 2.3945176535539093e-09, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cupping\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2084}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Rio Olympics\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"the marks\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"legs\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"shoulders\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have done cupping for a while before meets,\\\" Phelps said during the 2016 games.\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2245, \"end\": 2251, \"titl